@startuml

Title Navigation for finished Carport project

note top of Employee
Username and role
stored in session
end note
note top of Customer
Username and role
stored in session
end note

legend bottom center
All boxes represents jsp pages. Every jsp page goes to the Frontcontroller servlet which uses javaclasses called commands to do specific operations and navigate to the next jsp page
end legend

[*] --> customerindex #Salmon
[*] --> employeeindex #DodgerBlue


state Customer #Wheat {
customerindex --> customerpage #Salmon : Log in
customerpage --> customerpage : Edit customerdetails 
customerpage --> orderhistory #Salmon 
orderhistory --> customerorderinformation #Salmon : View specific order information 
customerorderinformation --> customerorderinformation : Pay for order 
customerorderinformation --> customertechdrawing #Salmon : Show technical drawing for specific order
customerorderinformation --> customerbillofmaterials  #Salmon : Show bill of materials for specific order
customerpage --> submitorder #Salmon 
submitorder --> orderconfirmation #Salmon
}

state Employee #Wheat {
employeeindex --> browseorders #DodgerBlue : Log in
browseorders --> browseorders : Update status on a specific order
browseorders --> orderinformation #DodgerBlue : Go to specific Order
browseorders --> browsematerials #DodgerBlue
orderinformation --> techdrawing #DodgerBlue : Show technical drawing for specific order 
orderinformation --> billofmaterials #DodgerBlue : Show bill of materials for specific order
browsematerials --> materialinformation #DodgerBlue : See specific material details
materialinformation --> materialinformatino #DodgerBlue : Edit material details
orderinformation --> orderinformation : Edit Order
}

Employee --> employeeindex : Through header
Customer --> customerindex : Through header 

Customer --> [*] : Log out
Employee --> [*] : Log out

@enduml
